beforeUploadingWeAskYouToGoOver.message: Before uploading, we ask you to go over the complete Unsplash submission guidelines.

thanksForContributingToUnsplash.message: Thanks for contributing to Unsplash! You’re awesome. To save you time and increase your chance of being featured, please ensure that your photos meet our submission guidelines.

onlyUploadHighQualityPhotos.message: Only upload high quality photos. For a standard landscape orientation photo, {minimumMegapixels, number} megapixels is at least {dimensionsWidth, number} by {dimensionsHeight, number} pixels in size.

photosAreStrongclearOriginal.message: Photos are clear, original and are not over edited. Photos do not contain nudity or violent imagery. Unsplash is a place for people of all ages.
